3.5.text:
When using the Service, it is strictly prohibited to: 
- impersonate another person or organisation, or otherwise mislead as to your identity; 
- hack, interfere with, or disrupt the Platform, distribute viruses or malicious code, run automated scripts or actions that impair normal Service operation; 
- bypass technical limitations, attempt unauthorised access to other accounts, restricted areas or other Users' data; 
- use the Platform for illegal activity, including fraud, money-laundering, financing prohibited organisations or any violation of law; 
- post prohibited content, including extremist or pornographic material, insults, threats, false information, spam advertising, or materials infringing intellectual-property or privacy rights; 
- harvest data about other Users or the Platform automatically (e.g., bots, scraping) without our written permission. 

Violation may result in measures up to suspension or blocking of the account without notice, removal of illegal content and notification of competent authorities.
